        <h2>About Chloë's Cocoon</h2>
        <p> Hello, I'm Chloë. In my free time, I'm an influencer for Asian products on tiktok, and during my normall day
            life I study digital design. I created this website to see the potential interest for Chinese-style dresses,
            a fashion niche I'm deeply passionate about. My love for these fairy-like, romantic dresses has always been
            strong, and finding such unique pieces in Europe has always been a challenge. This website is not just a
            one-time project; it's the beginning of a continuous journey to bring beautiful, enchanting dresses to those
            who share my appreciation for them.</p>

